{"id":"313160128_The_list_chromatic_number_of_graphs_with_small_clique_number","abstract":"We prove that every triangle-free graph with maximum degree $\\Delta$ has list chromatic number at most $(1+o(1))\\frac{\\Delta}{\\ln \\Delta}$. This matches the best-known bound for graphs of girth at least 5. We also provide a new proof that for any $r\\geq 4$ every $K_r$-free graph has list-chromatic number at most $200r\\frac{\\Delta\\ln\\ln\\Delta}{\\ln\\Delta}$.","authors":["Michael Molloy"],"meta":["January 2017Journal of Combinatorial Theory Series B 134(3)","DOI:10.1016/j.jctb.2018.06.007"],"references":["301270965_Harmonious_coloring_of_uniform_hypergraphs","290028654_Pathwidth_and_Nonrepetitive_List_Coloring","265681632_Problems_and_results_on_3-chromatic_Hypergraphs_and_some_related_questions","256091709_On_the_Facial_Thue_Choice_Number_of_Plane_Graphs_Via_Entropy_Compression_Method","226956676_On_Turan's_theorem_for_sparse_graphs","5915439_Phase_Transitions_in_the_Coloring_of_Random_Graphs","326022717_On_the_Lovasz_Theta_Function_for_Independent_Sets_in_Sparse_Graphs","306230159_Random_walks_that_find_perfect_objects_and_the_Lovasz_local_lemma","305522989_Random_Walks_That_Find_Perfect_Objects_and_the_Lovasz_Local_Lemma","280590567_Focused_Stochastic_Local_Search_and_the_Lov'asz_Local_Lemma","275279783_On_the_Lov'asz_Theta_function_for_Independent_Sets_in_Sparse_Graphs","262290265_Distributed_coloring_algorithms_for_triangle-free_graphs","244507082_The_choice_number_of_sparse_graphs","244462698_Graph_Colouring_and_the_Probabilistic_Method","244418327_Asymptotic_choice_number_for_triangle_free_graphs","230528678_The_list_coloring_constants","228115539_On_the_Facial_Thue_Choice_Index_via_Entropy_Compression","225279619_Acyclic_edge-coloring_using_entropy_compression","222472913_Coloring_Graphs_with_Sparse_Neighborhoods","222159459_A_note_on_the_independence_number_of_triangle-free_graphs","221590136_A_constructive_proof_of_the_Lovasz_local_lemma","220485463_A_constr